      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total stunner! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've pampered this beauty since day one, so it's flawless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, you've found it! Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
