    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no chips or swirls, having been preserved under a professional ceramic coating and kept in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine showroom condition; the premium leather is supple and free of any creasing, while every electronic component operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete service history from authorized specialists and a drive that is as tight and responsive as the day it was manufactured. This is a rare, collector-grade example for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
